Marking a section just marks all tracks in that section.
Leave point at the topmost affected track."
  (interactive "p")
  (or n (setq n 1))
  (if (< n 0)
      (bongo-mark-line-forward (- n))
    (dotimes (dummy n)
      (bongo-previous-object)
      (bongo-mark-line))))

(defun bongo-mark-region (beg end)
